AC-MTL16-003 FEATHER CLEANING EQUIPMENT

The washing line includes: 1 washing machine with double-wall drum design with mixing paddle, 1 handling podium with galvanized finish. The system is mounted on a frame structure made of lock-section and on a concrete platform. The drums are provided with stubs for the introduction and drainage of water. The washed feather is drained by means of a spigot with a valve handle. The drive is provided by a pulley drive motor.
The unit is made of corrosion-resistant steel.

Dimensions:
– length 3000 mm
– width 3160 mm
– height 2940 mm
– Wash drum: ø1500 mm

AS-MTL40-003 FEATHER LOADING SILO

Automatic weighed water feather feeder silo suspended on steel HEB support structure, with ultrasonic mass flow sensors, front/rear continuous silo belt, silo dome, suction fan. The feather with a nominal weight of 250 kg is fed into the drying unit according to the set weight value.

Unit material: painted metal support structure, Blockboard.

Dimensions:
– length: 2500mm
– width:1500mm
– height: 5400mm

BO-MTL16-003 FEATHER DRYING EQUIPMENT


The BO-MTL16-003 drying machine line is a thermo oil heated automatic drying machine for drying water fowl feathers. The drying temperature of up to 150°C guarantees a sufficiently dry, bacteria-free and high filling power feather. The unit has a nominal filling weight of 50kg (50% moisture content) of wet feathers and can produce up to 125kg of dry feathers per hour, in compliance with standards. The vapour from the feather is removed by a high-capacity fan. This vapour is filtered and dedusted in several stages before being released to the open air. The unit is thermally insulated and working safety is ensured by highly reliable opening and rotation sensors.


Unit weight: 11000 kg


Nominal speed of mixing blades: 80 f/min.


Dimensions:
– length: 6377mm
– width: 2400mm
– height: 3702mm

TH-MTL20-003 FEATHER COOLER

Feather cooling equipment (for high temperature feather cooling) with 2pcs double painted metal mixing half-cylinder, 2pcs bearing mounted mixing shaft, 2×16pcs mixing blades, driven by a belt transmission through a V-belt transmission by a front wheel drive motor.

Unit material: 70×70 mm longitudinal glued beam support structure, 18mm birch plywood

Dimensions:

– length: 4000 mm

– width: 2500 mm

– height: 2500 mm

 

TKP-CS15-000-4 FEATHER DUSTING - MIXING EQUIPMENT

Electronically controlled feather dusting-mixing machine with electronically balanced feeding silo, vacuum filters, bagging chamber with 2 filling heads (feather mixing, feather dedusting, feather and down separation)

Material of the unit: painted hollow section support structure, 12 mm plywood.

TO-BGO-600 THERMO OIL HEATING BLOCK

 

2 pcs 300kW heat generating unit with automatic control, gas detection equipment, distribution manifolds, pumps, storage/evacuation tanks, chemical, insulated pipework, fittings, preassembled in 20′ container.

Mechanical dewatering of feathers by rotation and pneumatic membrane.
Tank capacity: 45 hl
Automatic control cabinet with emergency stop. Press with touch screen (located on the front side, in the lower position) where the work process can be followed visually.

Unit material: corrosion-resistant steel rotating drum with press membrane.


Dimensions:

– height: 2026 mm
